# Originally the name of a {{de}} village, now merely an isolated [[street]] on a hill top outside the municipality of [[Kürten]] in the [[Bergish Land]], east of [[Cologne]].
# Proper name of a [[brook]] or [[creek]] near [[Kürten]] in the [[Bergish Land]] east of [[Cologne]] in [[Germany]].

